title: Week 5 Red Challenge Flag Picks & filling out the AFC playoff picture
itunes:title: Week 5 Red Challenge Flag Picks & filling out the AFC playoff picture
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined in the Stage 5 set alongside Matt "Money" Smith and Handsome Hank before the Week 5 games! The guys get into Zaxby's Fresh Takes by choosing who will get the remaining AFC playoff seeds outside of New England and Kansas City (8:10). Next up, continuing the topic from last DDFP, Shek asks Money and Hank which NFL mascot would they eat (26:53)? Then the trio makes fun of Eddie Spaghetti's Tweets because he went to a music festival over the weekend (33:23). Lastly, the group rounds out the show with their Week 5 Red Challenge Flag picks (37:22)!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
